    <briefdescription>
<para>Holds function pointers to pind RPC plugin functionality. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This structure should be allocated and returned by a plugin library in response to a call to <ref refid="group__PLUGIN_1ga841f2257a22717c7c4a016ff138dbee3" kindref="member">load_plugin</ref>.</para>
<para>This structure can be placed as the first member of a user declared structure to provide plugin specific additional state. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
